compo
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a compensation payment or allowance under the Workers Compensation Act (now Accident Compensation Commission) for an injury received in the course of employment; the compensation system in general; a compensation payment.
Origin:abbreviation
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
